<div class="arabic_hadith_full arabic">
<span class="arabic_sanad arabic"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">الله عنه ال‏:‏ ال ل الله لى الله ليه ‏لم ‏: </font></font></span>
<span class="arabic_text_details arabic"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">‏ ‏ " ‏لا ل الجنة ام‏" </font></font></span>
<span class="arabic_sanad arabic"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">‏ ‏(‏(متفق ليه)‏)‏.</font></font></span>
